Class ConfigListNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.AbstractConfigNode

  • Type Parameters:
    T - - Element type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigListElementNode, ConfigListValueNode

    public abstract class ConfigListNode<T>
extends ConfigElementNode
    Class represents a array of node elements.

    Node elements are expected to be of type com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.AbstractConfigNode or Strings (for value node).
